Money

Money is used to
- Pay for tributes.
- Pay for auctions.
- Pay for market items.
- Pay for other miscellaneous things. (ccs and other minor stuff)

Money can be earned by
- Talking in general chat. (base kit 5-15 coins, can be upgraded by upgrading office)
- Getting your salary. (You get 100 base kit every phase change, increased by upgrading forge)
- Gifts in battlechat. (100-300 coins)
- Stock market. (!info stock market)
- Bank. (!info bank)
- (If you're respawning) Gambling.
